T02D2890:241a-1: bha ga b'an badzra p'a ni sto tra /
T02D2890:241a-3: bcom ldan 'das phyag na rdo rje la bstod pa /
T02D2890:241a-4: dpal phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2890:241a-5: h'um bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
T02D2890:241a-7: gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad cing //
T02D2890:241a-8: stobs po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2890:241a-9: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
T02D2890:241a-11: ngag gi nyes pa 'joms mdzad pa //
T02D2890:241a-12: sngags rnams gsung la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2890:241a-13: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
T02D2890:241a-15: rnam rtog ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
T02D2890:241a-16: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2890:241a-17: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
T02D2890:241b-2: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2890:241b-3: las kyi gnod sbyin chen po rnams //
T02D2890:241b-4: 'jigs su rung ba'i cha byad can //
T02D2890:241b-5: ma lus thams cad 'jigs par byed //
T02D2890:241b-7: lcang lo can gyi gnas mchog dam pa na //
T02D2890:241b-8: gsang sngags rig sngags kun gyi bdag po ste //
T02D2890:241b-9: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
T02D2890:241b-10: bcom ldan rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
